al point symmetries\nstudied in the framework of special solutions of the Bohr Hamiltonian. The\nunderlying dynamical and quasi-dynamical symmetries are also discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Jul 2008 14:54:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-07-29"}
